  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Play at Your Own Pace!</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slow down time to evaluate the situation - then <strong>strike</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/26f0b5d76f53474e791771f1ce43078c.poster.avif?t=1737781324\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/26f0b5d76f53474e791771f1ce43078c.webm?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/26f0b5d76f53474e791771f1ce43078c.mp4?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or, dash your way through levels at supersonic speeds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/c429e2fbd01606f2dd89853cfebe7b0f.poster.avif?t=1737781324\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/c429e2fbd01606f2dd89853cfebe7b0f.webm?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/c429e2fbd01606f2dd89853cfebe7b0f.mp4?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Fight or Flight?</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slash your way through enemies and boss fights- watch out, three hits and you’re dead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/278c7617cfa0eb73c768a7f97e097740.poster.avif?t=1737781324\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/278c7617cfa0eb73c768a7f97e097740.webm?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/278c7617cfa0eb73c768a7f97e097740.mp4?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bind your foes together to take them out all at once!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Take in the Ambience.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awaken deep in the heart of a cavern and embark on your quest to save a life. Traverse 350+ rooms as you venture across the island of Stosia. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/c975bf11b15da64cbe8f1ff1ed555a38.poster.avif?t=1737781324\" width=480 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/c975bf11b15da64cbe8f1ff1ed555a38.webm?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/c975bf11b15da64cbe8f1ff1ed555a38.mp4?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Keep Your (Singular) Eye Out...</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt to find all 51 secret butterflies hidden throughout your adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/47ad572fecc50f43a1f5735bec1bc301.poster.avif?t=1737781324\" width=480 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/47ad572fecc50f43a1f5735bec1bc301.webm?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932570/extras/47ad572fecc50f43a1f5735bec1bc301.mp4?t=1737781324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
